content: That's a great list of recipe ideas! I think my friends would love the Cranberry Brie Bites and the Herbed Crusted Beef Tenderloin. For the 10-day stay with my family, I might try making the Chicken or Vegetable Tagine with Couscous. Can you give me some tips on how to make the tagine, like what type of chicken or vegetables to use and how to cook the couscous?
